00:43:12,819 --> 00:43:14,159
Hello?

560
00:43:14,159 --> 00:43:15,579
 Hello? Zhou Siyue.

561
00:43:15,579 --> 00:43:16,979
 Where are you?

562
00:43:19,639 --> 00:43:20,879
What's up?

