568
00:43:36,866 --> 00:43:39,087
You never reply to my messages.

569
00:43:39,879 --> 00:43:41,480
Doing experiments.

570
00:43:42,318 --> 00:43:44,479
But you can't always stay in the lab.

571
00:43:44,479 --> 00:43:45,500
How boring.

572
