Why don't you join our Anime &amp; Comics Club?

573
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:48,720
It's really fun.

574
00:43:50,110 --> 00:43:54,299
By the way, we just received a drawing competition invitation.

575
00:43:54,940 --> 00:43:56,139
A drawing competition?

576
00:43:56,139 --> 00:43:59,900
Yes. The winner will be signed by the press directly.

577
