582
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:09,959
But she refused.

583
00:44:09,959 --> 00:44:11,959
She said she didn't have time.

584
00:44:11,959 --> 00:44:16,700
I have no idea what could possibly keep a freshman like her so busy.

